HEADWORD: mosquitofish
<hw>mosquitofish</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A silvery topminnow
(<spn>Gambusia affinis</spn>) with rows of black spots of tropical North
America and West Indies; important in mosquito control.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> <spn>Gambusia affinis</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

